TITLE: Component Execution Order Control
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to control component execution order using before and after properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/aframevr/aframe/blob/master/docs/core/component.md#2025-04-23_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
AFRAME.registerComponent('foo', {
  after: ['bar'],
  // ...
  tick: function() {
    console.log('Called second');
  }
  // ...
});

AFRAME.registerComponent('bar', {
  before: ['foo'],
  // ...
  tick: function() {
    console.log('Called first');
  }
  // ...
});
```

