TITLE: Managing Entity States in A-Frame (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use removeState method to remove a state from an entity and listen for the stateremoved event.
SOURCE: https://github.com/aframevr/aframe/blob/master/docs/core/entity.md#2025-04-23_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
entity.addEventListener('stateremoved', function (evt) {
  if (evt.detail.state === 'selected') {
    console.log('Entity no longer selected.');
  }
});

entity.addState('selected');
entity.is('selected');  // >> true

entity.removeState('selected');
entity.is('selected');  // >> false
```

