TITLE: Removing Object3D from Entity in A-Frame (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates the use of removeObject3D method within a component's lifecycle to remove a THREE.Light object from the scene and update the object3DMap.
SOURCE: https://github.com/aframevr/aframe/blob/master/docs/core/entity.md#2025-04-23_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
AFRAME.registerComponent('example-light', {
  update: function () {
    this.el.setObject3D('light', new THREE.Light());
    // Light is now part of the scene.
    // object3DMap.light is now a THREE.Light() object.
  },

  remove: function () {
    this.el.removeObject3D('light');
    // Light is now removed from the scene.
    // object3DMap.light is now null.
  }
});
```

