TITLE: Registering a Custom Box Geometry in A-Frame JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to register a custom box geometry using AFRAME.registerGeometry. It defines the schema for the geometry's properties and initializes the geometry using THREE.BoxGeometry.
