CODE:
```
AFRAME.registerGeometry('box', {
  schema: {
    depth: {default: 1, min: 0},
    height: {default: 1, min: 0},
    width: {default: 1, min: 0},
    segmentsHeight: {default: 1, min: 1, max: 20, type: 'int'},
